{
  "text": "Tumoral genomic DNA (10 ng) was amplified in a 25 \u00b5L PCR reaction using the Pyromark PCR kit (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany); PCR and sequencing primers were obtained from Wang et al.'s published method [CITATION_1] . All experiments were performed as described by the authors.",
  "correct_citation": {
